N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 5601.8 - Issuance of registration

State Regulations

The commission shall notify an applicant in writing if
the commission grants a registration and shall add the trade name and entity
name of the registrant to a list the commission maintains on the commission's
website. Notes
